description._content: Description: 31. Same land as shown in 30 above showing thriving plantation established in background. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Description: 32. Marshland adjoining that shown in 30 above planted with fast growing Eucalyptus about 4 years old. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
